reviewText: Movie was very good, liked watching my favorite actor and his leading lady (also one of my favorites) in a very good screen play.
Classic Univeral Studios and James Whale movie...  The movie also explains why "The Mummy's Hand" sets looked so Mayan, not Egyptian...  Too bad this movie is in limited availability.

The movie was fine however the quality of the picture was poor. I was disapointed because I expected better. I paid way too much for a very bad print. Whoever copied this print came right off of TCM. Half way through a TCM logo appears. This is like a bootleg copy.
